Package at.tugraz.ist.ase.cacdr.checker

Interface IConsistencyChecker

All Known Implementing Classes:
ChocoConsistencyChecker
public interface IConsistencyChecker
A common interface for the different consistency checkers. Note that checkers must not modify any of the input parameters!
